{
  "name": "LockIn — Relances quotidiennes",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## LockIn × n8n — V4 Multi-Canal (Email, SMS & Les 2)\n\n**Variables n8n** (Settings → Variables) :\n- `CRON_SECRET` — identique à Vercel / lockin-web\n- `LOCKIN_API_URL` — ex. `https://lockin-web.online`\n- `LOCKIN_FROM_EMAIL` — expéditeur SMTP\n- `TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER` — numéro expéditeur SMS (E.164)\n\n**Credentials n8n :** SMTP + Twilio API\n\n**Flux :** Cron 08h Paris → GET relances → boucle → check-status (`id`) → aiguillage `channel` → envoi SMTP / Twilio (`continueOnFail`) → ack JS → si payé : ack `cancelled`.",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 480,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "fef435d4-59a7-43e1-aa09-b8960c2cc16a",
      "name": "Note de configuration",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 8 * * *"
            }
          ]
        },
        "timezone": "Europe/Paris"
      },
      "id": "78ae503b-18db-453a-b199-6f806e143a9c",
      "name": "1. Tous les jours 08h00",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [240, 400]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $env.LOCKIN_API_URL.replace(/\\/$/, '') + '/api/cron/relances-du-jour' }}",
        "authentication": "none",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
